TITLE: Executing Single Delivery Call with curl
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to make a single delivery call to the Adobe Target Delivery API for retrieving an experience for one mbox. It includes the request payload with user and context information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adobe/target-nodejs-sdk/blob/main/openapi/delivery/markdown/api-description.md#2025-04-23_snippet_12

